"<qt>You are about to sign user id:<br /><br />%1 (%2)<br />ID: %3<br /"
">Fingerprint: <br /><b>%4</b>.<br /><br />You should check the key "
"fingerprint by phoning or meeting the key owner to be sure that someone is "
